  "bio_raw": "Mr. Amiya Chowdhury has been teaching English Literature and Language for five years. He is a seasoned fiction writer and essayist. Prior to joining Center for Language Studies (CLS) of University of Liberal Arts (ULAB), he worked as a Lecturer at the Department of English (DEH) of ULAB for a year and a half. He authored two books, several short stories and essays, published in different renowned dailies and magazines.",
